{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0003","text":"當初多少錯愛 就敗在但求被愛","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","後悔","付出"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["錯愛","敗","被愛"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,4,4,2,2,2,2,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["co1","do1","co3","oi3","zau6","baai6","zoi6","daan6","kau4","bei6","oi3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"當初","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"多少","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"錯愛","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"就敗","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"但求","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"被","pos":"PART"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"反思過去的錯誤戀情，歸因於過度渴望被愛，語氣帶有自省與遺憾。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0004","text":"但你 我以生命來盛載","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","承諾","付出"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["生命","盛載"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,5,5,3,2,0,0,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","nei5","ngo5","ji5","sang1","ming6","loi4","sing4","zoi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我以","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"生命","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"來","pos":"PART"},{"text":"盛載","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"對比過去的失敗，強調現在願意付出一切來珍惜這段感情，語氣堅定。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
