{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0007","text":"天寵幸我 如神蹟創造你","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","幸運","緣分"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["天寵幸","神蹟","創造"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,2,5,0,0,3,3,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","cung2","hang6","ngo5","jyu4","san4","zik1","cong1","zou6","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"寵幸","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"神蹟","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"創造","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"形容遇見對方是上天的恩賜，如同神蹟，語氣充滿感恩與讚嘆。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0008","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
