{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0009","text":"何謂滿足 終於相信幸福不擔心過期","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","幸福","信任"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["滿足","幸福","過期"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,3,3,4,2,3,3,3,3,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho4","wai6","mun5","zuk1","zung1","jyu1","seon3","hang6","fuk1","bat1","daam1","sam1","gwo3","kei4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"何謂","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"滿足","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"終於","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"相信","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"幸福","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"擔心","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"過期","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"領悟到真正的滿足感，相信幸福不會因時間而消逝，語氣充滿頓悟與安心。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
