{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0012","text":"沒有艱難 怎彰顯決心","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","考驗","決心"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["艱難","彰顯","決心"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,0,9,3,9,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mut6","jau5","gaan1","naan4","zam2","zoeng1","hin2","kyut3","sam1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"艱難","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怎","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"彰顯","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"決心","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"提出設問，認為沒有經歷困難，就無法顯現出堅定的決心，語氣帶有哲理。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0013","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
