{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0014","text":"分享分擔你我 讓熱淚伴隨熱吻","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","分享","親密"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["分享","分擔","熱淚","熱吻"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,3,3,5,5,2,2,2,2,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["fan1","hoeng2","fan1","daam1","nei5","ngo5","joeng6","jit6","leoi6","bun6","ceoi4","jit6","man5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"分享","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"分擔","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"讓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"熱淚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"伴隨","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"熱吻","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描繪兩人共同經歷生活中的喜怒哀樂，情感交融，語氣親密而溫馨。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0015","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0015","text":"合襯 愛夠深自然合襯","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","契合","默契"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["合襯","愛夠深","自然"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,4,4,3,2,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hap6","can3","oi3","gau3","sam1","zi6","jin4","hap6","can3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"合襯","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"愛夠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"深","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"自然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"合襯","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"斷言兩人之間是天造地設的契合，深厚的愛意自然會帶來默契，語氣充滿自信。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0016","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0016","text":"未恨活得傳奇 平凡才是福氣","structure":{"line_index":16,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","平凡","幸福"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["平凡","福氣"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,2,3,0,0,0,0,0,2,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mei6","han6","wut6","dak1","cyun4","kei4","ping4","faan4","coi4","si6","fuk1","hei3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"未恨","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"活得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"傳奇","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"平凡","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"才","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"福氣","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"表達不再追求傳奇般的人生，認為平凡的生活才是真正的福氣，語氣趨於平淡與知足。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0015","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0017","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0017","text":"每秒也就如 浪漫鑽禧","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","時間","浪漫"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["每秒","浪漫","鑽禧"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,2,0,2,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mui5","miu5","jaa5","zau6","jyu4","long6","maan6","zyun3","hei1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"每秒","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"浪漫","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"鑽禧","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"將每一刻都比喻為「浪漫鑽禧」，形容時間的珍貴與愛情的永恆，語氣充滿詩意。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0018","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0018","text":"未用甜言蜜語 想討好你","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","真誠","付出"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["甜言蜜語","討好"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,2,0,0,2,5,9,9,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mei6","jung6","tim4","jin4","mat6","jyu5","soeng2","tou2","hou2","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"甜言蜜語","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"討好","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"表明不需要用虛假的甜言蜜語去取悅對方，語氣帶有真誠與自信。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0019","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0019","text":"用一生 迎合你","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","奉獻","承諾"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["一生","迎合"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,3,3,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jung6","jat1","sang1","jing4","hap6","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"迎合","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"直接表達願意用一生去順應和配合對方，語氣堅定而充滿奉獻。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0020","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0020","text":"天保佑我 拿餘生交給你","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","託付","信任"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["天保佑","餘生","交給"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,2,5,0,0,3,3,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","bou2","jau6","ngo5","naa4","jyu4","sang1","gaau1","kap1","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"保佑","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"拿","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"餘生","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"交給","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"祈求上天保佑，將自己剩餘的生命完全託付給對方，語氣充滿信任與依賴。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0021","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0021","text":"在你名下 平凡日子找到我的驚喜","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","平凡","驚喜"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["名下","平凡日子","驚喜"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,0,2,0,0,2,9,9,4,5,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoi6","nei5","ming4","haa6","ping4","faan4","jat6","zi2","zaau2","dou3","ngo5","dik1","geng1","hei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"名下","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"平凡","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"日子","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"找到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"驚喜","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"在對方的庇護下，即使是平凡的日子也充滿了意想不到的驚喜，語氣帶有幸福感。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0022","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0022","text":"何謂滿足 不知想要什麼卻未能沒你","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","依賴","需求"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["滿足","想要","未能沒你"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,3,3,3,9,4,2,3,4,2,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho4","wai6","mun5","zuk1","bat1","zi1","soeng2","jiu3","sam6","mo1","koek3","mei6","nang4","mut6","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"何謂","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"滿足","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不知","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"想要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"卻","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"未能","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"沒","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"再次探討滿足的定義，發現自己不再清楚確切的需求，但卻無法想像沒有對方，語氣帶有依戀。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0023","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0023","text":"明白快活哪可只倚靠自己","structure":{"line_index":23,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","依賴","自我"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["明白","快活","倚靠自己"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,2,5,9,9,9,4,2,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ming4","baak6","faai3","wut6","naa5","ho2","zi2","ji2","kaau3","zi6","gei2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"明白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"快活","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"哪","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"倚靠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"自己","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"領悟到真正的快樂並非完全依賴自己，而是與對方共同擁有，語氣帶有對關係的肯定。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0022","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0024","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0024","text":"能忘掉背後記憶 因眼前有你","structure":{"line_index":24,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","當下","珍惜"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["忘掉","記憶","眼前"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,2,2,4,3,3,5,0,5,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nang4","mong4","diu6","bui6","hau6","gei3","jik1","jan1","ngaan5","cin4","jau5","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"忘掉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"背後","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"記憶","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"因","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"眼前","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"重複句，再次強調因為有對方的存在，過去的記憶變得不再重要，專注於眼前的幸福，語氣肯定。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0023","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0025","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0025","text":"神懷着愛造世間 準我能愛你","structure":{"line_index":25,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","神恩","允許"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["神","愛造","世間","準","愛你"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,2,4,2,4,9,5,0,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["san4","waai4","zoek6","oi3","zou6","sai3","zeon2","ngo5","nang4","oi3","nei5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"神","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"懷着","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"愛造","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"世間","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"準","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"將愛情的發生歸因於神的創造與恩准，認為這份愛是神聖且被允許的，語氣充滿神聖感與感激。"},"source":{"title":"在你名下","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1083","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA4Mw_0024","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
